---
title: "Currency — Cuento Docs"
---

      <div class="docs-eyebrow">Admin Panel</div>
      <h1 class="docs-title">Currency</h1>
      <p class="docs-lead">
        The Currency page lets you define a site currency — its name and icon — and configure
        the income rules that automatically award currency to members for activity on the board.
      </p>

      <div class="docs-screenshot">
        <img src="/assets/screenshots/admin-currency.png" alt="Admin Currency page screenshot" />
      </div>

      <h2 class="docs-h2">Currency Settings</h2>

      <div class="field-list">

        <div class="field-row">
          <div class="field-meta">
            <div class="field-name">Name</div>
            <div class="field-values">text</div>
          </div>
          <div class="field-desc">
            The display name of the currency shown to members throughout the site.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="field-row">
          <div class="field-meta">
            <div class="field-name">Icon URL</div>
            <div class="field-values">text</div>
          </div>
          <div class="field-desc">
            URL of the image used as the currency icon. Paste a direct link to any publicly
            hosted image, for example one uploaded via ImgBB.
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <h2 class="docs-h2">Income Types</h2>
      <p class="docs-p">
        Each income type defines an event that triggers an automatic currency reward.
        Enter the amount to award in the number field and check the box to enable that rule.
        Uncheck to disable a rule without deleting its configured amount.
      </p>

      <div class="field-list">

        <div class="field-row">
          <div class="field-meta">
            <div class="field-name">Game post</div>
          </div>
          <div class="field-desc">
            Awarded for every individual in-character post a member writes.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="field-row">
          <div class="field-meta">
            <div class="field-name">100 / 500 / 1000 game posts</div>
          </div>
          <div class="field-desc">
            One-time milestone bonuses awarded when a member reaches 100, 500, or 1000 total game posts.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="field-row">
          <div class="field-meta">
            <div class="field-name">100 / 500 / 1000 general posts</div>
          </div>
          <div class="field-desc">
            One-time milestone bonuses awarded when a member reaches 100, 500, or 1000 total general (out-of-character) posts.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="field-row">
          <div class="field-meta">
            <div class="field-name">Character sheet accepted</div>
          </div>
          <div class="field-desc">
            Awarded when a member's character sheet is approved by staff.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="field-row">
          <div class="field-meta">
            <div class="field-name">Wanted character</div>
          </div>
          <div class="field-desc">
            Awarded when a member claims a character from the wanted characters list.
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="callout">
        If multiple post-count milestones apply at the same time (e.g. 100 &amp; 500, or 100, 500 &amp; 1000),
        only the largest reward will be granted.
      </div>

      <h2 class="docs-h2">Saving</h2>
      <p class="docs-p">
        Both the Currency Settings block and the Income Types block have their own
        <strong>Save</strong> button. Save each section independently after making changes.
      </p>
